Retrieve the list of domains you own.

USAGE:
  scw domain domain list [arg=value ...]

ARGS:
  [order-by]           (domain_asc | domain_desc)
  [registrar]         
  [status]             (status_unknown | active | creating | create_error | renewing | renew_error | xfering | xfer_error | expired | expiring | updating | checking | locked | deleting)
  [project-id]        
  [is-external]       
  [domain]            
  [organization-id]   

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for list
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use
